parameters: \F[3]\AA[F]Um... Didn't you return to the spirit world?

I intended to, but... It seems like some sort of mechanism is
preventing me from leaving this place.

There's a powerful barrier in place. Probably, only Lady Sadi and
Lady Merill can leave easily.
\F[10]\AA[F]I see... Do you have any idea how to deactivate it?

...I don't know. That's why I... \c[14]was searching for the weapons
storage room\c.

The \c[14]storage room\c, which used to be Anthurium's old haunt,
is not affected by this spell... That's why there should be a
clue to escape there.

\F[10]\AA[F](\c[14]If Hayato were here, \c he could probably
handle those weapons. If that were the case...)
Are you thinking of having Lord Hayato forcefully break through?

\F[15]\AA[F]Don't read my mind! I was also frustrated because I
was stuck searching for the code....

\F[10]\AA[F]..........Hey, Anthurium. Shall we go to the library
for a bit? I want to clear my head.
`知ってるヒトに会うと安心するわね...。アンはヒトじゃないけど...。`
